   "source": [
    "At this subcritical temperature and moderate pressure, the calculated phase is\n",
    "gas-like and considerably denser than air. The range assertion is deliberately broad:\n",
    "it detects unit, phase, or setup errors without presenting SRK as a reference-quality\n",
    "pure-CO₂ standard."
