    "## Independent low-pressure validation\n",
    "\n",
    "The current NeqSim regression suite records a Clapeyron reference density of\n",
    "3.3079 kg/m³ for pure CO₂ at 320 K and 2 bara. The EOS-CG implementation is accepted\n",
    "within 5% in that repository test. The same state is reproduced here and also compared\n",
    "with the ideal-gas limit."
   ]
