   "source": [
    "## Model comparison over transport pressure\n",
    "\n",
    "The following sweep uses 40 °C, above the pure-CO₂ critical temperature, to avoid\n",
    "crossing a vapor-liquid saturation line while comparing single-phase properties.\n",
    "Sixteen independent states are calculated for SRK, PR, and EOS-CG. Span–Wagner is\n",
    "evaluated separately at 80 bara, where the current release returned a finite stable\n",
    "state; it is not extended across a range that failed the finite-property gate."
   ]
